Privacy Policy for Instagram Reels Fix

Last updated: June 2026

Instagram Reels Fix does not collect, transmit, store, or share any personal information or browsing data.

Information Collection

This extension does not collect any of the following:

Personal information
Account credentials
Browsing history
Website content
Location information
Analytics data
Usage statistics
Local Storage

The extension stores user preferences locally in the browser using the Chrome/Opera storage API. These preferences are used solely to remember extension settings, such as whether the extension is enabled or disabled.

This information remains on the user's device and is not transmitted to any external server.

Third-Party Services

The extension does not communicate with external servers or third-party services.

Data Sharing

No data is sold, shared, or transferred to any third party.

Changes to This Policy

If the extension's data practices change in the future, this policy will be updated accordingly.

